          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped shallot </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 3 min or until softened</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for a further 1 min</p>",
